  "detailed_description": "Join two kindred spirits, Fargus the Jester and Nikki the acrobat in a fantastic 3D world of magic and mystery as they bounce, tumble and jump through 18 massive and diverse levels in search of the Wishing Engine!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced 3D platform action in a lush, texture-mapped environment.<br></li><li>Over 18 levels, hilarious power-ups, tons of secrets, huge bosses and shape-change from a bull-dozing rhino to a fire-blasting dragon.<br></li><li>A totally immersive experience complete with beautiful soundtrack and cinematics.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Join two kindred spirits, Fargus the Jester and Nikki the acrobat in a fantastic 3D world of magic and mystery as they bounce, tumble and jump through 18 massive and diverse levels in search of the Wishing Engine!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast-paced 3D platform action in a lush, texture-mapped environment.<br></li><li>Over 18 levels, hilarious power-ups, tons of secrets, huge bosses and shape-change from a bull-dozing rhino to a fire-blasting dragon.<br></li><li>A totally immersive experience complete with beautiful soundtrack and cinematics.</li></ul>",
